{"tid":252273,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人未試過比對方送返屋企？","createTime":"2017-05-21T14:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T07:50:07.000Z","uid":115454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c3287c07d82f39f60ea06cbde5d0463905f634b0","tid":252273,"uid":115454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:39:46.000Z","msg":"一齊左幾年 大家住得遠 一次都未試過比人送返屋企<br />\n明白住得遠 一來一回要佢搭幾個鐘車好唔人道 又好似冇咩需要咁 度度都咁多人 唔通真係怕比人捉走左咩 <br />\n但有時見到其他人有人送返屋企 內心都有啲羨慕 會諗到底比人送返去係咩感覺呢 係咪好sweet呢 <br />\n就算聚會完一齊走 永遠都係各有各走 有時都真係有dd唔開心 但諗起佢要搭好遠車 又唔忍心講出聲想佢送 但我諗就算講到出聲佢都未必肯..<br />\n巴打們願唔願意送女朋友返屋企？假如你地車程個幾鐘 我真係一次都未試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a685f6cfbf3a2545b135f9c3a226333a69eabb6","tid":252273,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:40:25.000Z","msg":"你個名"},{"pid":"6c742743776a1ff714753c85ba3a60e4612c4f97","tid":252273,"uid":104618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:43:50.000Z","msg":"要夜晚同埋第2日唔洗返工先會"},{"pid":"b0c2a9ab195502c5c262cab2cb2dc461d71ca42d","tid":252273,"uid":115454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T15:01:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個名</blockquote><br />\n岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然覺得佢都對我好好 好似"},{"pid":"cc716ff3e30a3e312268a2178c916e1aababe3bc","tid":252273,"uid":115454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T15:05:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要夜晚同埋第2日唔洗返工先會</blockquote><br />\n夜晚都唔會 <br />\n以前都會行遠少少送下我搭巴士 依家連送下去搭巴士都冇 安慰自己佢攰姐<br />\n但同fd食糖水又夜都肯 好似岩岩咁 明明一齊走 我要搭好遠車 佢幾個站就到 同行朋友問食唔食糖水我夜同遠所以話唔食 佢就去左食 送多我幾個站都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係囉送我就遠啲 食糖水就近啲"},{"pid":"1da8bc0799315d76bca206f8e31fa528d8b8d906","tid":252273,"uid":5937,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T15:05:55.000Z","msg":"除非對方自願送啦 唔係都咪制<br />\n盞雙方都唔好受 對方送得心不甘情不願<br />\n你又幻想落空咁有乜意思呢"},{"pid":"fc06da80b41ed7d249317d74ac0881f4af2b33a4","tid":252273,"uid":115454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T15:13:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除非對方自願送啦 唔係都咪制<br />\n盞雙方都唔好受 對方送得心不甘情不願<br />\n你又幻想落空咁有乜意思呢</blockquote><br />\n但幾年都冇送過..有時真係有少少唔開心"},{"pid":"2f59bbc81322ad2727e483b23c6735785c6e8417","tid":252273,"uid":94452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T15:17:20.000Z","msg":"依啲都係睇自覺性姐，可能佢覺得你唔會出事就唔送，但係送女朋友返去真係唔懶得既事黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6dc64103ea87b1c8648bfb0101253553fa5a65d","tid":252273,"uid":52875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T15:19:13.000Z","msg":"單程個幾鐘真係好撚遠<br />\n<br />\n果日有揸車咪"},{"pid":"d39eae88a3d093c39b524631a793da3764c3ade5","tid":252273,"uid":52875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T15:20:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>單程個幾鐘真係好撚遠<br />\n<br />\n果日有揸車咪送<br />\n冇揸車咪唔送囉</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c7ffb7fe3e2100e8803ba3884309671de906e976","tid":252273,"uid":65041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T15:23:05.000Z","msg":"有女一定送(如果地鐵到)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05396b344bc22c59396089f5f6bdacf2893c8160","tid":252273,"uid":80954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T15:41:57.000Z","msg":"一個做新界西，一個住新界東。<br />\n佢成日想送我，但我次次都唔肯，覺得大家各自送啲番屋企休息準備聽日番工仲好啦。拍拖"},{"pid":"02d084bfccdb205775c024121343609947ded5dd","tid":252273,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T15:42:51.000Z","msg":"香港地邊度要幾個鐘車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca46fe6e2bb399f6a266cf5f860aa85a5e0071f6","tid":252273,"uid":80954,